data.description: *Price Improvement* Come check out this beautiful Craftsman home offering a perfect blend of location and comfort! This property features an open floor plan with huge gourmet kitchen with gas stove, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, oversized kitchen island and peninsula with tons of extra seating. It also has a separate laundry with washer/dryer included. Upstairs provides features like walk-in storage, a Jack and Jill bathroom, walk-in closets in both bedrooms and large separate bonus room. The backyard has custom landscaping and a vinyl privacy fence, patio and custom wood deck. The patio furniture (front/back), umbrella and gas firepit are all included! Sellers are moving out of state and are highly motivated! Don’t miss out on this like new pristine home!
